commitResults.messageTitle: Refactor code to adhere to coding principles
commitResults.messageBody:
Tag and untag command do not adhere to law of demeter.

New method is added in ModelManager class to ensure so
that tag and untag command do not have to invoke a method
in Person class. Corresponding test cases are also added.

commitResults.messageTitle: Add test cases for tag and untag command
commitResults.messageBody:
Not enough code pushed is covered by tests.

Test cases are added to verify that new tagExists
method behaves correctly under execute method to
throw exceptions when needed.

Use of boolean wrapper is redundant and costs extra overhead.

Return type of tagExists method is changed to primitive boolean type.

Previous UML class diagram is outdated as pre-existing features
have been changed and new features have been added.

Changes to such features are now reflected in
BetterModelClassDiagram now.

Tag name example given to user includes a space.
There is no constraint on the length of tag name,
leading to visibility issues on UI.

White spaces are now allowed in tag names.
Tag is now limited to 30 characters.

Minimum test coverage is not met.

Test on ParserUtil class is added.
